<br>
&quot;I have reset my claw and put into evades and nanos and will go for a bow&quot;.<br>
<br>
I have breed maxxed my evades, nanoskills and bowskills and clawskills and parry etc. I use a ql177 bow and do up to 2800 dmg AS in pvp.<br>
<br>
But....<br>
<br>
The bow is all I can use in towerbattles. I rarely get any oppurtunity to actually fight against an opponent so I run around trying to AS ppl.<br>
<br>
I basically suck at tower battles and I am most useful as support to a soldier or trader. Helping with healings and, with a great deal of luck, doing some damage. So it doesn't matter what skills we put into, we are toast anyway!<br>
<br>
